sentence: On 9 June 1892 the Paris Opéra-Comique staged Les Troyens à Carthage (in the Théâtre de la Ville as its premiere) and witnessed a triumphant debut for the 17-year-old Marie Delna as Didon, with Stéphane Lafarge as Énée, conducted by Jules Danbé; these staged performances of Part 2 continued into the next year.
